Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.63,0:00:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请说出可爱东西的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.70,0:00:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.72,0:00:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,金发少女
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.97,0:00:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…小猫咪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.88,0:00:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.79,0:00:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个 那个 小忍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.11,0:00:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝~
